1
00:00:00,240 --> 00:00:05,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So please, until I move on...</font>

2
00:00:03,190 --> 00:00:06,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font size="12"><font face="Arial"><font color="#4d4737">Band Club</font></font></font></font>

3
00:00:03,190 --> 00:00:06,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font size="16"><font face="Impact"><font color="#d8d2d3">Auditioning for vocals</font></font></font></font>

4
00:00:05,020 --> 00:00:11,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's meet at our usual place.</font>

5
00:00:14,940 --> 00:00:19,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw, shucks, don't stare. 
You're making me nervous.</font>

6
00:00:19,210 --> 00:00:21,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's an audition, you idiot.</font>

7
00:00:21,190 --> 00:00:22,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's funny.</font>

8
00:00:22,740 --> 00:00:24,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This audition is a joke.</font>

9
00:00:24,730 --> 00:00:26,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, anyone else?</font>

10
00:00:31,590 --> 00:00:33,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asa-chan!</font>

11
00:00:33,090 --> 00:00:35,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cool. You're up, Takumi-san.</font>

12
00:00:39,440 --> 00:00:44,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Without you, Makio-chan, I probably 
wouldn't have joined the band club.</font>

13
00:00:44,360 --> 00:00:46,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think so.</font>

14
00:00:46,650 --> 00:00:48,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You made that decision yourself.</font>

15
00:00:48,980 --> 00:00:54,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think you would've arrived at that 
no matter who you were with.</font>

16
00:00:58,990 --> 00:01:03,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder what Mom and Dad would have said.</font>

17
00:01:04,050 --> 00:01:05,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not sure.</font>

18
00:01:06,500 --> 00:01:07,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe give it some thought.</font>

19
00:01:08,330 --> 00:01:10,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So I imagine...</i></font>

20
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:13,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good grief. What did you do to your hair?</font>

21
00:01:14,050 --> 00:01:17,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, just do what you want to do.</font>

22
00:01:18,360 --> 00:01:20,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What would they have said today?</i></font>

23
00:01:22,250 --> 00:01:25,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I still have no clue.</i></font>

24
00:01:26,860 --> 00:01:31,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess you... stood out.</font>

25
00:01:31,520 --> 00:01:34,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't know you liked to stand out.</font>

26
00:01:34,140 --> 00:01:38,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It means you've put in the work.</font>

27
00:01:38,520 --> 00:01:42,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is standing out a good thing? 
Or is it a bad thing?</font>

28
00:01:42,370 --> 00:01:47,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I dunno. I guess it feels wrong.</font>

29
00:01:47,480 --> 00:01:49,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like I'm just not the type.</font>

30
00:01:49,530 --> 00:01:51,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What?! Your </i>type<i>?!</i></font>

31
00:01:51,880 --> 00:01:54,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Who gives a crap about that?</i></font>

32
00:01:55,090 --> 00:01:57,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've carried a lot of regret about that.</i></font>

33
00:01:57,440 --> 00:02:01,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I got so caught up in the labels 
that before I knew it,</i></font>

34
00:02:01,060 --> 00:02:06,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I lost sight of what I actually
 wanted for myself.</i></font>

35
00:02:07,070 --> 00:02:08,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't get any of it.</i></font>

36
00:02:10,590 --> 00:02:13,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If anyone gives you a hard 
time for standing out...</font>

37
00:02:14,810 --> 00:02:16,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give them hell.</font>

38
00:02:17,080 --> 00:02:19,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't get that bit either.</i></font>

39
00:02:19,660 --> 00:02:24,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But as long as I'm alive, 
I might as well struggle.</font>

40
00:02:25,470 --> 00:02:28,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't get what you're saying at all!</font>

41
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:33,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I don't understand, I might as well...</i></font>

42
00:02:37,500 --> 00:02:40,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm gonna sing!</font>

43
00:02:46,830 --> 00:02:53,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#3b3132">Journal with Witch</font></font></font></font>

44
00:04:12,580 --> 00:04:14,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh? Lunch?</i></font>

45
00:04:12,810 --> 00:04:18,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Arial"><font size="14"><font color="#0d2f05"><b>Huh? Lunch?</b></font></font></font></font>

46
00:04:14,490 --> 00:04:16,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I guess. With my mom.</i></font>

47
00:04:14,640 --> 00:04:18,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Arial"><font size="14"><font color="#333334"><b>I guess. With my mom</b></font></font></font></font>

48
00:04:16,850 --> 00:04:18,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wha?</i></font>

49
00:04:18,570 --> 00:04:20,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So </i>that's<i> why she isn't here.</i></font>

50
00:04:18,770 --> 00:04:26,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Arial"><font size="14"><font color="#0d2f05"><b>So that's why she isn't here</b></font></font></font></font>

51
00:04:20,640 --> 00:04:22,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They seem to get along.</i></font>

52
00:04:20,780 --> 00:04:26,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Arial"><font size="14"><font color="#333334"><b>They seem to get along</b></font></font></font></font>

53
00:04:22,530 --> 00:04:26,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="14"><font color="#0d2f05"><b>Lol</b></font></font></font></font>

54
00:04:24,400 --> 00:04:26,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Then wanna come over?</i></font>

55
00:04:24,860 --> 00:04:26,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Arial"><font size="14"><font color="#0d2f05"><b>Then wanna come over?</b></font></font></font></font>

56
00:04:26,030 --> 00:04:31,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Arial"><font size="14"><font color="#0d2f05"><b>Then wanna come over?</b></font></font></font></font>

57
00:04:26,870 --> 00:04:28,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sorry, I have plans.</i></font>

58
00:04:27,030 --> 00:04:31,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Arial"><font size="14"><font color="#333334"><b>Sorry, I have plans</b></font></font></font></font>

59
00:04:29,180 --> 00:04:30,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Okay.</i></font>

60
00:04:39,060 --> 00:04:40,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm bored.</font>

61
00:04:43,010 --> 00:04:45,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="12"><font color="#b8bc57"><b>Three-Year Journal</b></font></font></font></font>

62
00:04:45,870 --> 00:04:49,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Wow, I've passed this place so many times.</font>

63
00:04:45,970 --> 00:04:50,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="12"><font face="Georgia"><font color="#ffffff">Episode 12\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h<font size="18">Find</font></font></font></font></font>

64
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:52,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I never noticed it before.</font>

65
00:04:52,340 --> 00:04:55,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so spacious and bright.</font>

66
00:04:55,370 --> 00:04:57,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't it?</font>

67
00:04:57,040 --> 00:05:00,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a little on the loud side,
but there are always open tables.</font>

68
00:05:01,710 --> 00:05:03,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Hamburg steak sounds good.</font>

69
00:05:03,690 --> 00:05:06,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is. It's pretty beefy.</font>

70
00:05:07,430 --> 00:05:08,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Beer...</font>

71
00:05:09,640 --> 00:05:12,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't daytime beers the best?</font>

72
00:05:12,640 --> 00:05:14,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's such a guilty pleasure.</font>

73
00:05:14,460 --> 00:05:15,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I'll have one.</font>

74
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:19,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh man, then I'm in too.</font>

75
00:05:20,830 --> 00:05:24,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wish we'd stopped here when we 
cleared out Asa's old place.</font>

76
00:05:27,540 --> 00:05:29,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That must have been hard.</font>

77
00:05:29,590 --> 00:05:30,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess.</font>

78
00:05:30,810 --> 00:05:33,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How long did it take?</font>

79
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:34,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A week?</font>

80
00:05:34,710 --> 00:05:37,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, maybe a little longer.</font>

81
00:05:37,310 --> 00:05:38,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

82
00:05:38,960 --> 00:05:44,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thinking back on it, I should've come
 by your place too to introduce myself.</font>

83
00:05:44,930 --> 00:05:47,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It didn't occur to me at the time.</font>

84
00:05:47,140 --> 00:05:49,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You didn't need to do that.</font>

85
00:05:50,710 --> 00:05:54,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was pretty shaken back then myself.</font>

86
00:05:54,210 --> 00:05:58,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Had I seen your face, 
I might have burst out crying.</font>

87
00:05:59,460 --> 00:06:01,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I resemble my sister?</font>

88
00:06:05,470 --> 00:06:07,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just your face.</font>

89
00:06:07,960 --> 00:06:08,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Just?"</font>

90
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:14,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It would've been like suddenly coming 
face-to-face with the departed.</font>

91
00:06:14,340 --> 00:06:16,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like a kind of vertigo.</font>

92
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:21,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think it might've scared me at the time.</font>

93
00:06:23,170 --> 00:06:24,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah...</font>

94
00:06:25,730 --> 00:06:30,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been experiencing less
 of that lately myself.</font>

95
00:06:32,050 --> 00:06:36,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Although Asa might need more time.</font>

96
00:06:46,870 --> 00:06:47,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello.</font>

97
00:06:51,380 --> 00:06:54,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just happened to be 
in the area for a meeting.</font>

98
00:06:54,430 --> 00:06:58,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. And I just happened to be
visiting someone in the hospital.</font>

99
00:06:58,640 --> 00:07:02,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then this was a series of coincidences.</font>

100
00:07:02,170 --> 00:07:05,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. I'm glad I invited you here.</font>

101
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:09,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Indeed, this might've been
our only chance.</font>

102
00:07:09,640 --> 00:07:12,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Er, I don't mean to imply
 I'd rather not have come.</font>

103
00:07:12,790 --> 00:07:15,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry. I know what you meant.</font>

104
00:07:15,870 --> 00:07:18,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who ordered the daily special?</font>

105
00:07:18,590 --> 00:07:19,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here.</font>

106
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:22,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't like sharing food?</font>

107
00:07:22,310 --> 00:07:24,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Must make going out in groups hard.</font>

108
00:07:24,980 --> 00:07:29,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. Thankfully, my current 
office is fairly laid-back.</font>

109
00:07:29,300 --> 00:07:32,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I had a lot of trouble in college.</font>

110
00:07:32,780 --> 00:07:34,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, college, of course.</font>

111
00:07:34,970 --> 00:07:37,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All those get-togethers.</font>

112
00:07:37,230 --> 00:07:41,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've always hated being 
pressured into drinking.</font>

113
00:07:41,460 --> 00:07:44,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hear you. They weren't my thing either.</font>

114
00:07:44,830 --> 00:07:50,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I managed to brush it off,
 but that doesn't seem your style either.</font>

115
00:07:51,070 --> 00:07:52,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Exactly!</font>

116
00:07:52,790 --> 00:07:56,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd end up getting upset 
at people every time.</font>

117
00:07:56,280 --> 00:07:58,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eventually, no one invited me anymore.</font>

118
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:01,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I guess it worked out?</font>

119
00:08:01,970 --> 00:08:03,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd say so.</font>

120
00:08:04,010 --> 00:08:07,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wasn't too happy about it back then.</font>

121
00:08:08,180 --> 00:08:12,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But that sort of crowd 
has always passed me over.</font>

122
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:14,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In a sense, I consider myself lucky.</font>

123
00:08:15,740 --> 00:08:17,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As a bookworm who can't read the room.</font>

124
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:20,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"That sort of crowd"?</font>

125
00:08:20,770 --> 00:08:24,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">People who align 
with male-centric rituals, I guess.</font>

126
00:08:24,670 --> 00:08:28,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Those of you becoming second-years,
 remember you're upperclassmen now.</font>

127
00:08:28,940 --> 00:08:32,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}You're the bridge between 
the first-years and third-years.</font>

128
00:08:32,100 --> 00:08:35,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Not just in games, 
but in everyday practice.</font>

129
00:08:32,370 --> 00:08:34,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, where's Yoshimura?</font>

130
00:08:35,580 --> 00:08:36,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Beats me.</font>

131
00:08:35,700 --> 00:08:38,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Make sure you're setting a 
good example. That's all!</font>

132
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:39,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir!</font>

133
00:08:40,610 --> 00:08:43,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That reminds me of an interaction 
I had with Asa-san.</font>

134
00:08:44,240 --> 00:08:47,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">During our meeting the other day,</font>

135
00:08:47,830 --> 00:08:51,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">she asked me how to become 
the person she wants to be.</font>

136
00:08:53,310 --> 00:08:54,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The person she wants to be?</font>

137
00:08:55,430 --> 00:08:57,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, sweet adolescence.</font>

138
00:08:57,340 --> 00:08:59,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, what'd you tell her?</font>

139
00:09:00,130 --> 00:09:02,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, actually...</font>

140
00:09:02,760 --> 00:09:05,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't know what she meant.</font>

141
00:09:06,510 --> 00:09:09,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I said, "I don't understand."</font>

142
00:09:09,680 --> 00:09:11,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jeez!</font>

143
00:09:11,870 --> 00:09:13,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Was that bad?</font>

144
00:09:14,400 --> 00:09:17,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, it's funny, I guess.</font>

145
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:18,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Funny?</font>

146
00:09:19,370 --> 00:09:21,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who you want to be, huh?</font>

147
00:09:22,340 --> 00:09:25,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How should I have answered, do you think?</font>

148
00:09:25,050 --> 00:09:25,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm...</font>

149
00:09:26,750 --> 00:09:28,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who you want to be...</font>

150
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:30,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course.</font>

151
00:09:32,060 --> 00:09:34,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should have stayed 
composed, just like that.</font>

152
00:09:36,300 --> 00:09:38,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Always so cool and collected.</font>

153
00:09:38,640 --> 00:09:41,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? You mean me?</font>

154
00:09:42,130 --> 00:09:43,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not like that at all.</font>

155
00:09:44,250 --> 00:09:45,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, but you are.</font>

156
00:09:46,180 --> 00:09:48,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I sure wish I were.</font>

157
00:09:50,090 --> 00:09:54,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if I honestly come off that way,
it might be because...</font>

158
00:09:54,690 --> 00:09:56,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know, what you said...</font>

159
00:09:56,780 --> 00:09:59,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hopped off that bandwagon.</font>

160
00:09:59,530 --> 00:10:00,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What I said?</font>

161
00:10:01,100 --> 00:10:03,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Male-centric rituals.</font>

162
00:10:03,580 --> 00:10:05,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or something like that.</font>

163
00:10:06,400 --> 00:10:09,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once I decided not to take part,</font>

164
00:10:09,800 --> 00:10:12,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">everything suddenly 
started getting easier.</font>

165
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:16,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who can do the scariest dare?</font>

166
00:10:17,190 --> 00:10:20,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who can objectify girls the most?</font>

167
00:10:21,070 --> 00:10:25,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who can gain the most 
while trying the least?</font>

168
00:10:25,740 --> 00:10:28,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even though I was being crushed
by the pressure deep down,</font>

169
00:10:28,250 --> 00:10:29,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd laugh it off.</font>

170
00:10:29,390 --> 00:10:31,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was the only crowd I knew.</font>

171
00:10:31,570 --> 00:10:35,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I clung for dear life
 to keep my standing.</font>

172
00:10:36,500 --> 00:10:40,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And all the while, I had the potential 
to be anyone I wanted.</font>

173
00:10:40,190 --> 00:10:45,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't realize that game of chicken 
was no real measure of my value.</font>

174
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:47,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quit crying! You're a man!</font>

175
00:10:47,570 --> 00:10:50,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I jumped off the 
bandwagon and ran away.</font>

176
00:10:50,650 --> 00:10:55,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think it finally made me human.
 It gave me a backbone.</font>

177
00:10:56,110 --> 00:10:57,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm fine with whatever you want.</font>

178
00:10:58,290 --> 00:11:00,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do what I want either way.</font>

179
00:11:00,850 --> 00:11:02,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you should do the same.</font>

180
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:07,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since I spent so much time 
adjusting myself to others,</font>

181
00:11:07,950 --> 00:11:12,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm drawn to people who can't 
help but do things their way.</font>

182
00:11:12,860 --> 00:11:15,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">People who are genuinely 
true to themselves.</font>

183
00:11:17,740 --> 00:11:19,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So that's where Koudai-san comes in!</font>

184
00:11:19,890 --> 00:11:20,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

185
00:11:20,750 --> 00:11:22,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You meant Koudai-san, didn't you?</font>

186
00:11:22,190 --> 00:11:24,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, yeah, but...</font>

187
00:11:24,850 --> 00:11:26,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That makes total sense.</font>

188
00:11:28,340 --> 00:11:30,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's grab daytime beers again sometime!</font>

189
00:11:31,690 --> 00:11:32,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course.</font>

190
00:11:33,040 --> 00:11:36,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't be a stranger. 
Send Asa to spend the night anytime.</font>

191
00:11:36,890 --> 00:11:40,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to help in any way I can.</font>

192
00:11:41,760 --> 00:11:43,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

193
00:11:44,130 --> 00:11:46,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think...</font>

194
00:11:46,950 --> 00:11:49,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It may take some time,</font>

195
00:11:49,620 --> 00:11:55,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but bit by bit, she'll have 
to figure things out on her own.</font>

196
00:11:55,900 --> 00:11:57,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Arrive at her own answers.</font>

197
00:11:59,210 --> 00:12:00,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so glad.</font>

198
00:12:01,780 --> 00:12:02,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For Asa-chan.</font>

199
00:12:03,380 --> 00:12:06,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so glad you're in her life.</font>

200
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:10,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who she wants to be...</font>

201
00:12:10,930 --> 00:12:14,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If Asa-san keeps grappling 
with that question, I wonder</font>

202
00:12:15,160 --> 00:12:18,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">if she'll eventually become 
cool and collected.</font>

203
00:12:19,570 --> 00:12:21,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd certainly like to see that.</font>

204
00:12:21,520 --> 00:12:24,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right? I can't wait.</font>

205
00:12:36,960 --> 00:12:39,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#000000">Journal with Witch</font></font></font></font>

206
00:12:41,010 --> 00:12:45,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I found myself alone, 
standing on an open page.</font>

207
00:12:45,940 --> 00:12:49,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter where I look, I can't see.</font>

208
00:12:49,340 --> 00:12:53,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no path, nor exit...</font>

209
00:12:53,670 --> 00:12:55,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Am I being too loud?</font>

210
00:12:55,540 --> 00:12:58,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I was just thinking how good you are.</font>

211
00:13:01,420 --> 00:13:07,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You welcome love with open arms, 
but compliments don't sit right?</font>

212
00:13:07,330 --> 00:13:09,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I dunno.</font>

213
00:13:09,840 --> 00:13:11,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that song for your band?</font>

214
00:13:11,610 --> 00:13:14,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup, we perform the day 
after opening ceremonies.</font>

215
00:13:14,220 --> 00:13:15,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your grand debut.</font>

216
00:13:16,280 --> 00:13:19,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's only for a little bit 
during lunch and after school.</font>

217
00:13:19,340 --> 00:13:20,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's great.</font>

218
00:13:21,430 --> 00:13:22,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

219
00:13:22,720 --> 00:13:23,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

220
00:13:24,150 --> 00:13:26,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">About writing lyrics...</font>

221
00:13:26,470 --> 00:13:27,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah?</font>

222
00:13:27,990 --> 00:13:30,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why do you always perk up 
when this comes up?</font>

223
00:13:30,950 --> 00:13:34,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love seeing people 
try their hand at a new craft.</font>

224
00:13:34,990 --> 00:13:36,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't get it.</font>

225
00:13:37,150 --> 00:13:38,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well?</font>

226
00:13:39,370 --> 00:13:41,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How do I get better at it?</font>

227
00:13:42,500 --> 00:13:46,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know, I haven't, like, 
totally given up on it.</font>

228
00:13:48,100 --> 00:13:51,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm... What if you tried writing 
out your favorite lyrics?</font>

229
00:13:51,730 --> 00:13:53,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like copying sutras.</font>

230
00:13:53,680 --> 00:13:54,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sutras...</font>

231
00:13:55,590 --> 00:13:58,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you've got your journal.</font>

232
00:13:58,760 --> 00:14:02,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why don't you try being 
intentional with it?</font>

233
00:14:02,570 --> 00:14:04,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Intentional how?</font>

234
00:14:04,660 --> 00:14:06,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

235
00:14:06,460 --> 00:14:08,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Makio-chan...</font>

236
00:14:08,450 --> 00:14:12,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Remember when you told me that journal 
entries don't have to be true?</font>

237
00:14:13,500 --> 00:14:14,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

238
00:14:14,580 --> 00:14:17,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">About my journal. A year ago.</font>

239
00:14:18,290 --> 00:14:19,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I said that?</font>

240
00:14:19,490 --> 00:14:21,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

241
00:14:21,040 --> 00:14:22,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I did...?</font>

242
00:14:22,990 --> 00:14:25,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I took that to heart, you know?!</font>

243
00:14:25,690 --> 00:14:28,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, then that's good, right?</font>

244
00:14:28,710 --> 00:14:29,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've ruined it now.</font>

245
00:14:30,350 --> 00:14:35,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like, imagine I royally screw up during 
our band's street performance.</font>

246
00:14:35,680 --> 00:14:37,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't say that. It's bad luck.</font>

247
00:14:37,690 --> 00:14:39,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just saying <i>if</i>...</font>

248
00:14:39,140 --> 00:14:44,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does that mean I could write in my 
journal that I <i>didn't</i> screw up?</font>

249
00:14:44,250 --> 00:14:47,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Hmm?</font>

250
00:14:47,400 --> 00:14:52,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if you ever read it back, wouldn't 
that remind you of how you <i>did</i> screw up?</font>

251
00:14:52,570 --> 00:14:53,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right.</font>

252
00:14:54,130 --> 00:14:57,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I probably didn't mean that 
you should write lies.</font>

253
00:14:57,920 --> 00:15:02,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hang on, did I really say you didn't 
need to write the truth?</font>

254
00:15:02,370 --> 00:15:04,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pretty much.</font>

255
00:15:05,660 --> 00:15:09,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I had to guess, I think it 
was less about what to write</font>

256
00:15:09,660 --> 00:15:12,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and more about what not to write.</font>

257
00:15:13,770 --> 00:15:15,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But who knows?</font>

258
00:15:18,360 --> 00:15:21,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After all, I don't remember.</font>

259
00:15:21,030 --> 00:15:25,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At the end of the day, as long as you're
not lying to yourself, it's probably fine.</font>

260
00:15:26,640 --> 00:15:30,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's weird. Isn't it bad to lie at all?</font>

261
00:15:31,900 --> 00:15:34,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I make a living off of lying.</font>

262
00:15:34,600 --> 00:15:35,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You weirdo!</font>

263
00:15:36,400 --> 00:15:39,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh, what if I screw up 
during the performance?</font>

264
00:15:39,380 --> 00:15:42,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop saying that.
Like I said, it's bad luck.</font>

265
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:47,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I only have vocal practice 
today, so I won't be late.</font>

266
00:15:47,330 --> 00:15:48,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

267
00:15:48,710 --> 00:15:50,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay then, I'm off...</font>

268
00:15:53,350 --> 00:15:54,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

269
00:15:55,610 --> 00:15:56,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen...</font>

270
00:15:57,520 --> 00:16:02,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you think Mom's journal is all true?</font>

271
00:16:02,740 --> 00:16:03,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

272
00:16:07,130 --> 00:16:10,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As if you'd ever answer
 a question like that...</font>

273
00:16:10,500 --> 00:16:11,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

274
00:16:11,400 --> 00:16:14,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing. I'll never know anyway.</font>

275
00:16:14,070 --> 00:16:15,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm off!</font>

276
00:16:15,770 --> 00:16:17,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have a good day.</font>

277
00:16:18,890 --> 00:16:20,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I think...</i></font>

278
00:16:20,940 --> 00:16:26,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It may take some time, but bit by bit,</font>

279
00:16:26,300 --> 00:16:29,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">she'll have to figure 
things out on her own.</font>

280
00:16:30,170 --> 00:16:32,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Arrive at her own answers.</font>

281
00:16:35,410 --> 00:16:37,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I said that, but...</font>

282
00:16:37,730 --> 00:16:41,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder if those answers even exist.</font>

283
00:17:04,960 --> 00:17:06,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="10"><font color="#605a54"><b>Uniform Point Deductions for Female Applicants:
Nitto Medical University Accused of Arbitrary Manipulation</b></font></font></font></font>

284
00:17:51,920 --> 00:17:55,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="8"><font color="#bc767a"><b>Performance</b></font></font></font></font>

285
00:18:01,930 --> 00:18:03,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asa, your turn in the bath.</font>

286
00:18:08,300 --> 00:18:10,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asa? What are you doing?</font>

287
00:18:11,260 --> 00:18:13,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Makio-chan, check it out.</font>

288
00:18:19,380 --> 00:18:21,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow.</font>

289
00:18:23,250 --> 00:18:24,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's all this?</font>

290
00:18:24,820 --> 00:18:26,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought I could make it my room.</font>

291
00:18:26,850 --> 00:18:28,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where'd you get it all?</font>

292
00:18:28,460 --> 00:18:29,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mostly the 100-yen store.</font>

293
00:18:29,920 --> 00:18:32,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Except the lantern. That was kinda pricey.</font>

294
00:18:32,740 --> 00:18:34,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been collecting stuff 
little by little.</font>

295
00:18:35,430 --> 00:18:39,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, and I want to put a shelf 
on the wall. Is that okay?</font>

296
00:18:39,340 --> 00:18:41,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, sure. Of course.</font>

297
00:18:42,230 --> 00:18:43,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm sorry.</font>

298
00:18:44,420 --> 00:18:45,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That I don't have another bedroom.</font>

299
00:18:45,900 --> 00:18:48,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's okay. It is what it is.</font>

300
00:18:48,800 --> 00:18:50,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, I'm impressed.</font>

301
00:18:51,490 --> 00:18:53,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know I said you could do 
whatever you wanted,</font>

302
00:18:53,800 --> 00:18:55,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I didn't expect this.</font>

303
00:18:56,190 --> 00:18:57,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's your own palace.</font>

304
00:18:58,840 --> 00:19:01,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, are you going to sleep in here?</font>

305
00:19:01,660 --> 00:19:05,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought about it, 
but I can't stretch my legs out.</font>

306
00:19:05,480 --> 00:19:08,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I'll sleep out here like always.</font>

307
00:19:08,000 --> 00:19:09,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

308
00:19:09,970 --> 00:19:12,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why? Am I in the way?</font>

309
00:19:12,960 --> 00:19:14,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm used to it.</font>

310
00:19:16,150 --> 00:19:22,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. So this is how you find your 
own way of life, piece by piece.</font>

311
00:19:22,930 --> 00:19:26,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? You're complicating things again.</font>

312
00:19:27,710 --> 00:19:31,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, and another thing I've 
been thinking about...</font>

313
00:19:32,160 --> 00:19:34,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about if we make it their birthdays?</font>

314
00:19:35,660 --> 00:19:37,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean for my mom and dad.</font>

315
00:19:37,970 --> 00:19:39,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Their birthdays?</font>

316
00:19:39,780 --> 00:19:41,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't really...</font>

317
00:19:41,980 --> 00:19:46,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">want it to be the day they d-died.</font>

318
00:19:47,410 --> 00:19:51,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're coming up on the anniversary
of your parents' death.</font>

319
00:19:52,600 --> 00:19:57,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you want to do something for it,
we'll fit that in too.</font>

320
00:19:58,580 --> 00:20:04,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My mom and dad's birthdays were close,
so we always celebrated between them.</font>

321
00:20:05,330 --> 00:20:08,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apparently, that's how 
they first got close.</font>

322
00:20:08,760 --> 00:20:10,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh.</font>

323
00:20:12,370 --> 00:20:16,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sis was born on April 10th. And your Dad?</font>

324
00:20:16,380 --> 00:20:18,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">April 13th.</font>

325
00:20:18,260 --> 00:20:20,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That is really close.</font>

326
00:20:20,070 --> 00:20:20,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup.</font>

327
00:20:20,970 --> 00:20:22,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

328
00:20:22,570 --> 00:20:23,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think?</font>

329
00:20:24,250 --> 00:20:28,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then let's do it on April 11th or 12th.</font>

330
00:20:29,160 --> 00:20:33,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll get a nice cake and buy candles</font>

331
00:20:33,100 --> 00:20:37,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to celebrate their birthdays together.</font>

332
00:20:37,380 --> 00:20:38,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

333
00:20:40,590 --> 00:20:43,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say, this idea of yours...</font>

334
00:20:44,240 --> 00:20:47,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think it's brilliant. Really brilliant.</font>

335
00:20:47,650 --> 00:20:48,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean it?!</font>

336
00:20:49,370 --> 00:20:52,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I do. Sincerely.</font>

337
00:20:52,520 --> 00:20:54,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

338
00:21:05,940 --> 00:21:06,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Makio-chan?</font>

339
00:21:08,740 --> 00:21:10,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go on and take a bath.</font>

340
00:21:10,460 --> 00:21:11,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll get dinner ready.</font>

341
00:21:11,920 --> 00:21:13,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">'Kay.</font>

342
00:21:17,850 --> 00:21:19,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How strange...</font>

343
00:21:20,060 --> 00:21:21,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not even her parent.</font>

344
00:21:28,390 --> 00:21:34,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I keep giving water 
to my own loneliness,</i></font>

345
00:21:36,890 --> 00:21:40,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>could a flower bloom 
in the dead of night?</i></font>

346
00:21:51,740 --> 00:21:53,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="12"><font color="#adaf50"><b>Three-Year Journal</b></font></font></font></font>

347
00:21:52,470 --> 00:21:57,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A train is arriving on platform 3.</i></font>

348
